Name:           Power Element
Short Name:     power
Level Required: 23

Description:
  The mightiest of all Elementals, the Power Element elecrifies foes
  and summons bolts of lightning to strike them.

Commands:
  - summon power:   Summons it to you         (costs 150 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban power:      Banishes it               (costs 35 sp)
